Class TerminalDialog

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TrayTerminalDialog

    public abstract class TerminalDialog
extends JFrameConnectionDialog
implements Destroyable
    This implements a very dumb terminal. The terminal understands backspace, newline and carriage return. The terminal is also capable of producing standard arrow key escapes.
